Bazaarvoice,is,a,social,marketing,company,that,helps,clients,to,integrate,social,data,across,their,entire,organization,The,Bazaarvoice,Platform,lets,businesses,capture,and,analyze,customer,conversations,to,help,drive,campaigns,The,Bazaarvoice,Platform,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,functionality,of,the,Platform,including,customer,reviews,in,their,own,web,sites,and,application,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formated,in,XML,and,JSON,Full,documentation,requires,registration